name: d/riediger - Nov. 5, 2011 - Namecoin
description:
d/riediger

Mint date: Nov. 5, 2011, 5:11 p.m.

Minted in 2011 on namecoin, this NFT of the text "riediger" happens to be one of the earliest NFTs to ever exist in blockchain history!

One of the earliest NFT's in history.

Namecoin is the first fork of Bitcoin & the only altcoin to which Satoshi Nakamoto had himself contributed. Popular projects on NMC include Twitter eggs, Blockheads, Manga avatars, Identicons, Punycodes etc.
